        <ol type='a'>
          <li>NTT for education and research purposes: (<a href="http://NTT_RE@tiaer.tarleton.edu">http://ntt_re@tiaer.tarleton.edu</a>)</li>
          <li>Last version of NTT: (<a href="http://nn.tarleton.edu/nttg2">nn.tarleton.edu/nttg2</a>)</li>
        </ol>
        <li>A watershed scale model titled "Comprehensive Economic Environmental Optimization Tool (CEEOT): CEEOT" is available to download from www.tiaer.tarleton.edu. CEEOT is an integrated program that includes APEX, SWAT and Farm Economic Model (FEM) models to evaluate the economic and environmental impacts of conservation practices at the farm and watershed scales. CEEOT is not an internet-based  model. To obtain more information and/or download a copy of CEEOT program, please visit www.tiaer.tarleton.edu.</li>
      </ol>
    </p>
  </div>
